| Risk | Impact | Likelihood | Mitigation | Owner |
|---|---|---:|---|---|
| Citation gaps (Article 21A; RTE updates) | Potential doctrinal misalignment | Medium | Add official sources; flag items needing update | Content Lead |
| Jurisdiction nuance (High Court vs Supreme Court) | Over/under-specific remedy questions | Medium | Generalize writ jurisdiction; add contextual notes | QA Lead |
